Thanks so much, ghostvs. I have never trusted anyone that didn't have the skull and crossbones next to their name, but something told me this was legit. It downloaded in like 10 minutes NO KIDDING! And the quality is absolutely flawless. Only thing is that it says the maker of the film at the bottom in white letters. It's in the black though so it doesn't take away from the movie. :)
